INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (1,'2025-12-01 15:14:02.039372','Unleash Your Passion for Speed and Style with the THALASI Supra Oversized T-Shirt Elevate your wardrobe with a t-shirt that speaks volumes. The THALASI Men\'s Oversized T-Shirt is more than just clothing; it\'s a statement piece designed for the modern man who values comfort, style, and a nod to legendary automotive engineering. Fusing the world of JDM car culture with contemporary streetwear, this tee is your ticket to effortless cool. A Tribute to a Legend The heart of this t-shirt is the stunning, high-quality Supra graphic printed on the back. It’s a bold homage to one of the most iconic cars ever made, designed to turn heads and connect you with a community of fellow enthusiasts. Whether you’re a gearhead or simply appreciate a powerful design, this back-printed tee sets you apart from the crowd. Engineered for Ultimate Comfort We believe style should never come at the expense of comfort. That’s why we crafted this t-shirt from 100% premium bio-washed cotton. The fabric is incredibly soft and breathable, making it perfect for the Indian climate. The oversized fit with down shoulders provides a relaxed, non-restrictive feel, giving you the freedom to move, whether you\'re hitting the gym for a workout or just cruising through your day. Style It Your Way The timeless black color and versatile design make this round-neck t-shirt a powerhouse in your closet. Streetwear Look: Pair it with cargo pants or distressed jeans and your favorite sneakers. Gym Ready: The breathable cotton and relaxed fit make it the perfect gym t-shirt for men\'s workouts. The THALASI Promise We are committed to delivering superior quality. From the rich, fade-resistant print to the durable, reinforced stitching, every detail is meticulously crafted to ensure you get a product that not only looks great but also lasts long. Add the THALASI Supra Oversized T-Shirt to your cart NOW and drive your style to the next level!','61091000'